  "title": "Logistics Executive (Wed - Sun | East)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Oversee shipping documentation and track all shipment movements, including POD updates, to ensure timely delivery.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with internal teams, external partners, and logistics planners to forecast shipments, plan deliveries, and streamline the order-to-delivery process.</li>\n  <li>Manage damaged shipment claims and liaise with warehouse, facility, and finance teams on operational matters such as recycling and supplier invoicing.</li>\n  <li>Build strong relationships with vendors and cross-functional teams to support business growth and operational efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Monitor material inflow and product outflow to meet customer timelines while ensuring full compliance with customs, trade, and cross-border shipping regulations.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and deliver regular logistics performance reports on a weekly and monthly basis.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
